{"tid":2376205,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣女兒趙克露 獲拜登委任美國國際媒體署代理執行長","createTime":"2021-01-22T15:10:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T12:37:54.000Z","uid":200280,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fb96a236e4ea0e34cb50631dd35eb4b0e3f7884a","tid":2376205,"uid":200280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T15:10:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AkGkk5x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAkGkk5x.jpg&h=6528789e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拜登任命曾擔任美國之音代理總台長的趙克露（Kelu Chao）出任代理執行長職務。<br />\n<br />\n趙克露的父親是前中央日報副社長趙俊廷，民國99年3月23日在美國馬里蘭州以88歲高齡辭世時，中華民國政府還曾頒贈褒揚令，表彰他對台灣新聞的貢獻，趙克露可謂是克紹箕裘。<br />\n<br />\n趙克露在台灣時曾就讀中山女高、政大新聞系，畢業後赴美攻讀教育與媒體，在肯特大學畢業後進入美國之音工作至今。<br />\n<br />\n美國國際媒體署是美國聯邦政府負責對外廣播事務的獨立機構，負責管理美國之音、古巴廣播辦公室等機構，並監管自由歐洲電台、自由亞洲電台等非營利機構。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/121687/5194498\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F121687%2F5194498&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5BVTfDkzAunSCULMKrq9Td0%3D&h=b02b1bc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/121687/5194498</a>"},{"pid":"3011dd18806b642b8974ee2666762e854ba589c8","tid":2376205,"uid":200280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T15:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eqN7LAm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeqN7LAm.png&h=99bd87f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d277dc8f6cf4095e1058b9503f7d75eb71abde0","tid":2376205,"uid":200280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T12:37:54.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}